# In_Progress Folder

Contains items currently being worked on by specific agents.

## Structure

```
In_Progress/
├── email_agent/
│   └── active_tasks.md
├── social_media_agent/
│   └── active_tasks.md
├── accounting_agent/
│   └── active_tasks.md
└── whatsapp_agent/
    └── active_tasks.md
```

## Example: Agent Claim File

```markdown
---
agent: email_agent
claimed_at: 2026-03-09T11:00:00Z
task_type: email_response
original_file: Needs_Action/email_123.md
status: in_progress
---

## Current Task

Responding to invoice request from client@example.com

## Steps Completed

- [x] Read email content
- [x] Generated invoice PDF
- [ ] Send email with attachment
- [ ] Move to Done folder

## Estimated Completion

2026-03-09T11:15:00Z
```

## Purpose

- Prevents multiple agents from processing the same item
- Tracks agent activity and progress
- Enables debugging and audit trail
